00:27:09,490 --> 00:27:13,370
The old you is you, and the current you is also you.

358
00:27:13,370 --> 00:27:16,370
I loved you then, and I love you now.

359
00:27:16,370 --> 00:27:19,330
Just you. Yoon Ji Won.

