00:27:48,570 --> 00:27:50,320
What?

368
00:27:50,320 --> 00:27:52,580
I was there next to you.

369
00:27:57,970 --> 00:27:59,800
By chance...

370
00:28:00,590 --> 00:28:03,690
did you visit me at the hospital?

371
00:28:04,390 --> 00:28:06,080
Yeah.

372
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:10,200
And you're the one who rescued me?

