379
00:28:32,860 --> 00:28:38,940
♫  Still, I think of you  ♫

380
00:28:38,940 --> 00:28:41,740
So, Miss Yoon Ji Won,

381
00:28:42,740 --> 00:28:45,750
please stay off the rooftop.

382
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:50,240
You should've told me that you came by then.

383
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:52,340
You should've told me you were there.

384
00:28:52,340 --> 00:28:55,680
Do you know how much I missed you then?

385
00:28:56,790 --> 00:28:58,470
I know.

